This mod contain the following changes:
- Logistic growth ceiling increased
- Habitability for auto migration increased
- Assimilation don't promote authoritarianism
- Ethics job modifiers of egalitarian and xenophile switched (localisation not updated accordingly)
- Galactic doorstep last event now triggered correctly
- Civilians from high living standards now generate resources as jobs, not strata
- Slavery allowed on subspecies of main species
- AI will prefer living standards utopian > decadent > good
- AI will check consumer goods overflow to change to higher living standards (pendent)